cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL

The paper discusses experiments on training and testing hidden units in deep networks with discrete activations, which is a topic closely related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also investigates simple classification and regression tasks (cs.AI), as well as memorization and compression problems (cs.CV, cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.NE and cs.AI. The sub-categories cs.CV and cs.CL are less likely but still relevant due to the specific tasks investigated in the paper.
